Requirements:

- Python from http://www.python.org (tested with Python 2.5) (package python)
- Django from http://www.djangoproject.com/ (package python-django)
- lxml from http://codespeak.net/lxml/index.html (package python-lxml)
- Daisy Pipeline from http://www.daisy.org/projects/pipeline/ (use the Pipeline Core Packages)


